Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.82,0:12:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}That the day would come that Saku\Nwould bring her friends over...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.93,0:12:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know, Saku...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.62,0:12:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Well then, if you will...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.33,0:12:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}The bathroom is here! And this is the toilet!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.04,0:12:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think you need to show around\Nevery single room, you know....
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.42,0:12:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}And then the second floor is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.86,0:12:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.19,0:13:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.61,0:13:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So, this is Loli-chan's room, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.73,0:13:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very feminine-like.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.27,0:13:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.10,0:13:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And you have lots of clothes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.21,0:13:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,P-Papa and Mama send me lots of them\Nevery month from abroad, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.85,0:13:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, shall we get started with\Ntoday's main subject right away?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.04,0:13:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Loli-chan's fashion study group!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.48,0:13:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-thank you in advance for your help!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.54,0:13:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, for starters, shall we have you\Ntake off everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.07,0:13:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.37,0:13:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ev-{\alpha&HFF&}ery-thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.22,0:13:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ev-ery-{\alpha&HFF&}thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.56,0:13:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ev-ery-thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.29,0:13:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.18,0:13:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Momoi-san, shall we learn about\Nhow to doubt people as well today?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.02,0:13:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.50,0:13:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! Kanade, don't you get in the way now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.62,0:13:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Someya-san, you are one...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.03,0:13:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad I came along.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.50,0:13:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So, which is it? Do I take it off? Or don't take it off?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.59,0:13:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- Take it off!\N- Don't take it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.38,0:13:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Someya-san! You are taking your jesting a little too far!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.76,0:13:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You know, it's unfair for you\Nto suddenly get so close like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.02,0:13:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, forget about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.18,0:14:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Once more, it's the start of the study group!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.52,0:14:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Loli-chan, when a girl like you, who's short in height,\Nwants to wear a long skirt, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.61,0:14:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Miracle change!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.18,0:14:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Your top should be accented with color\Nand make the bottom a high waist!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.38,0:14:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,By doing this, you style up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.88,0:14:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You are cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.16,0:14:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Next up is, overalls, which tend to\Nend up looking rather rustic...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.33,0:14:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Miracle change!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.73,0:14:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,By slipping on a long cardigan,\Nyou turn into a relaxed-cute fashionista!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.46,0:14:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.29,0:14:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You are relaxed-cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.67,0:14:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You coordinate a boyish-look with girly hair\Nto create a gap in styles.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.18,0:14:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,S-so cute...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.30,0:14:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,In addition, something like this, where you\Nloosely wear a course-knit one-piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.04,0:14:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,See, even just this is cute, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.10,0:14:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly! You're too cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.23,0:14:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh! I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.49,0:14:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap... We haven't said\Nanything but cute for a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.09,0:14:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.07,0:14:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,there is simply no other way to describe her...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.91,0:14:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,God is unfair, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.89,0:14:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.05,0:14:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been blessed with a body to this degree,\Nso how dare you ask for more!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.08,0:14:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You big-boobed buster!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.33,0:14:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,B-Buster?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.34,0:15:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,At times, obsequiousness and modesty can\Nirritate people, you know. So, keep that in mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.13,0:15:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,M-My apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.70,0:15:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That was lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.92,0:15:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Majime, do you want to study\Nhow to become cuter too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.05,0:15:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Well, of course, if I could be,\Nthen I'd want to, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.64,0:15:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let's do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.14,0:15:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go to Majime's house right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.63,0:15:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and then Majime, you can have\Na fashion study group too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.02,0:15:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds good! Let's go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.77,0:15:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.29,0:15:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw! I'm hungry! Let's eat something!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.99,0:15:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.68,0:15:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! Salted green onion kalbi bowl?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.88,0:15:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You're kidding me!\NObviously, something like that's gonna be tasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.56,0:15:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?! Damn it! How dare they season it with\Nsesame oil! Well of course it's tasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.87,0:15:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what're you having over there?\NHuh?! A soft-boiled egg pork cutlet bowl?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.21,0:15:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,There it is! How dare they think they can\Njust make it a soft-boiled egg...! Fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.54,0:15:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Soft-boiled gooeyness is like righteous!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.96,0:15:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.13,0:15:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}When Wota consumes something delicious,\N{\an8}she loses it, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.13,0:15:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, it's delicious! Not to mention, it's pork loin!\NIt's gonna be invincible dripping with fat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.17,0:15:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Robo, what's yours?! A juicy deep-fried bowl?!\NAre you kidding me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.38,0:15:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It even has tartar sauce over it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.34,0:15:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's totally breaking the rules! It's like the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.10,0:16:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.68,0:16:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,My friends are here to hang out right now, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.86,0:16:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, they all really want to meet you, Big Sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.90,0:16:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So, she's Kohaku-chan's older twin sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.38,0:16:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Then that means she's the same age as us, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.49,0:16:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Do they look alike then?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.46,0:16:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.57,0:16:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Then go ahead and make it sound like I've died.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.78,0:16:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I will not!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.74,0:16:22.46,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Today's visitations have ended\N{\an8}(except Kohaku).
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.49,0:16:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry. Big Sis is considerably shy, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.50,0:16:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Sister, wanna chat with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.04,0:16:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's hang out together!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.58,0:16:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Sis, it's not scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.88,0:16:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! A translucent Michael Jackson!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.63,0:16:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.76,0:16:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! So cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.84,0:16:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So alike!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.72,0:16:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! You tricked me, Kohaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.35,0:16:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.14,0:16:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah! Big Sis is very good at fortune telling!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.85,0:16:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.56,0:16:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.39,0:16:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What kinda fortune telling?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.00,0:16:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And, there you go...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.42,0:16:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! Amazing! She nailed it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.98,0:16:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Then I want you to read my fortune next!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.53,0:16:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}O-okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.53,0:16:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if I can get a boyfriend by Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.63,0:16:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Me first...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.90,0:17:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The time is coming soon,\Nwhen the one inside me is going to awaken...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.50,0:17:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.86,0:17:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't...! Rage inside of meeeeeee!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.75,0:17:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.48,0:17:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're not gonna eat your meal right away,\NI'm gonna clean it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.88,0:17:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.21,0:17:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanade's friends? Come in. Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.18,0:17:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-thank you for having us over...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.10,0:17:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.57,0:17:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez. If you'd told me sooner,\Nthen I would've baked a cake or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.60,0:17:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Th-This is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.61,0:17:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my apologies. Shall I go buy one\Nat the cake shop in front of the train station?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.61,0:17:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But that place's fresh whipped cream\Nis a little off, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.24,0:17:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yum! They're like an extravagant salmon-ikura bowl!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.41,0:17:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7}Salmon\NIkura
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.20,0:17:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.95,0:17:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So elastic!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.05,0:17:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.04,0:17:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, she's so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.47,0:17:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, of course she's cute, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.21,0:17:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,This girl over here is super pretty too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.59,0:17:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez! Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.04,0:17:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw! It's fine! I'm having them share\Ntheir youthful essence with me, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.47,0:17:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Oh...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.72,0:18:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Someya-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.97,0:18:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Now then, once again, the fashion study group starts!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.73,0:18:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,First off, let us take a look at Kanade's closet!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.69,0:18:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.07,0:18:14.23,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\an7}Sweats
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.23,0:18:14.40,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\an7}Sweats\N{\an7}Shirts
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.40,0:18:14.57,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\an7}Sweats\N{\an8}Shirts\N{\an7}Shirts
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.57,0:18:14.78,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\an7}Sweats\N{\an8}Shirts\N{\an8}Shirts\N{\an7}Shirts
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.78,0:18:15.15,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\an7}Sweats\N{\an8}Shirts\N{\an8}Shirts\N{\an7}Shirts\N{\an8}Shirts
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.15,0:18:15.78,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\an7}Sweats\N{\an8}Shirts\N{\an9}Sweats\N{\an8}Shirts\N{\an7}Shirts\N{\an8}Shirts
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.86,0:18:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you a middle school boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.76,0:18:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not good at thinking up coordinated outfits, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.71,0:18:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,In general, I make do with about two or three styles.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.91,0:18:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You are a middle school boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.29,0:18:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Lily, I'm begging you! Please save Majime!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.56,0:18:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,When you plead that desperately,\Nthat does hurt my feelings, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.47,0:18:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got no choice. We'll go shopping\Nfor clothes again some other time and...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.12,0:18:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's make today a study group about hair styles!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.53,0:18:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.34,0:18:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.13,0:18:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.34,0:18:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,For short hair that tends to end up too boyish...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.90,0:18:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Miracle change!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.14,0:18:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Braided arrangement!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.64,0:18:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do something like this on my own...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.77,0:18:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Silky straight with an iron!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.76,0:18:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do this on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.52,0:18:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,A pompadour-style arrangement with a hair pin!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.03,0:18:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't feel like I could do this on my own...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.15,0:18:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! Majime, you're cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.03,0:19:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,H-huh... But it's not something\Nthat I could do on my own at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.91,0:19:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Hey! What's with that "I can't do this\Non my own" thing you keep saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.16,0:19:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if someone else does it for me,\Nthen I could possibly change temporarily,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.98,0:19:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,but I guess I'm saying that there's no point\Nif I can't do it on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.42,0:19:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey you! Do you think the girls of the world\Njust naturally become cute or something?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.55,0:19:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone makes an effort, you know! Effort!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.01,0:19:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the same as that studying you're so good at!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.01,0:19:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hey! Wait! Please... Don't knead them...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.39,0:19:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Oh...! Ah...! Not... Not there...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.39,0:19:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you dangling both of these tremendous things\Nwithout knowing something like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.85,0:19:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Well?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.76,0:19:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Majime!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.58,0:19:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.64,0:19:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It is just as you say, Someya-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.94,0:19:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that without a doubt, the women of\Nthe world naturally acquired fashion senses.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.85,0:19:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I will try to make a little more effort to do so...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.99,0:19:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Majime! Let's do our best together!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.91,0:19:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.22,0:19:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine if you understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.41,0:19:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,A child who so disliked fashion is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.41,0:19:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Let's master fashion together!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.41,0:19:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Until we're called fashion leaders!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.41,0:19:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}The influence from friends is amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.62,0:19:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,If I make an effort, I'll be able to become\Nbig like you, Majime, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.04,0:19:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}(T-h-a-n-k y-o-u.){wait what? wtf is this?}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.21,0:19:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If you make an effort, then for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.67,0:20:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.16,0:20:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,M-me too. I really learned a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.76,0:20:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.92,0:20:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels like all we've done is\Njust receive your help, Someya-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.96,0:20:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We should reciprocate in some way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.43,0:20:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus, I haven't shown my gratitude\Nfor the bras and eyebrow stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.02,0:20:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What? I already received a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.44,0:20:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.36,0:20:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, that would be...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.11,0:20:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Lots of...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.54,0:20:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Side... {\alpha&FF&}dish... es!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.12,0:20:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Side... dish... {\alpha&FF&}es!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.64,0:20:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Side... dish... es!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.16,0:20:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But since I can't say that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.25,0:20:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The fun memories I have of both of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.00,0:20:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,S..Someya-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.44,0:20:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Lily! You're a super good person!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.11,0:20:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you'll continue to be there for me, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.51,0:20:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.94,0:20:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Likewise!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.01,0:20:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! I'm gonna work harder to be fashionable!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.43,0:20:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Wota, what's up with her this time...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.99,0:20:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop that. I'm at my limit in a lot of ways right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.37,0:20:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the actual person in question...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.49,0:21:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,apparently knows she might have\Ngone too far this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.69,0:21:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,In terms of those bangs...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.95,0:21:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of becoming fashionable...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.95,0:21:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Last night, I was up until midnight studying the\Nfashion site that you told me about, Someya-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.87,0:21:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Loli-chan's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.90,0:21:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Loli-chan, morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.63,0:21:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.58,0:21:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... Good mo-
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.84,0:21:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! You guys! Don't you be hurting\NLoli-chan's feelings like that again!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.15,0:21:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's best if you think about\Ndeoxyribonucleic acid, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.60,0:21:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Just what exactly happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.33,0:21:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You look cute like a kokeshi doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.41,0:21:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Grandma, please give me your bangs!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.46,0:21:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,There you go talking nonsense again. This child...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.42,0:22:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Noisy and loud
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.09,0:22:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But also endearing
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.01,0:22:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The laughter from that day
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.85,0:22:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,A story that can't be rewound
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.85,0:22:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The thing about youth is, it's always light and shadows
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.73,0:22:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Inside the darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.78,0:22:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,A shining inferior star
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.03,0:22:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking back are complicated
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.53,0:22:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Far too beautiful days
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.54,0:22:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Springtime has always passed by unexpectedly by then
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.55,0:22:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Your words reverberate in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.60,0:23:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Someday springtime will take it all away
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.10,0:23:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Until that day, being stupid is all right
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.11,0:23:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I'll run past it
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.58,0:23:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.20,0:23:19.71,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\an8}LIKE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.20,0:23:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.71,0:23:24.42,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\an7}Stop being\N{\an7}so clingy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.71,0:23:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Long blond hair and sanpaku eyes.\NYounger in age delinquent bottom!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.75,0:23:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Black-haired glasses-wearing average Joe.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.34,0:23:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Crybaby working adult member of society\Nand bullied child, who's a top?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.21,0:23:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}That's playing dirty!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.13,0:23:39.02,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(978,864)}In the middle of \Nconsuming something delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.84,0:23:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Is there anyone who wouldn't like that?\N{\an8}On the contrary! Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.72,0:23:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hurry up and get married!\N{\an8}Let me deposit gift money to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.35,0:23:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}For crying out loud, get buried in the same plot!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.44,0:23:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'll even buy the grave! Hurry up and\N{\an8}let me deposit money for you! Thank ya!
